"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "5053: responsibility, for God's world",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5053",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All humanity has a moral obligation under God to one another, whether as national leaders, ministers, spouses, parents, children, believers or simply as human beings. This moral obligation is shown in the Scriptures to also include the animal kingdom and the environment.</p>\n<h2>The responsibility of national leaders</h2>\n<h3>To reward good and punish evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3-Rom13:4\">ROM 13:3–13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:12\">PRO 16:12</a></p>\n<h3>To administer justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:4-Prov31:5\">PRO 31:4–31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:8–31:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:19\">DEU 27:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:14\">PRO 29:14</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of Christian leaders</h2>\n<h3>To care for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:15-John21:17\">JHN 21:15–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">ACT 20:28</a></p>\n<h3>To preach, teach and handle the Scriptures properly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:6\">EZK 33:6</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of those who are married</h2>\n<h3>To love each other</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:4\">TIT 2:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>To mutually honour each other</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22\">EPH 5:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1\">1PE 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of parents to their children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:24\">PRO 13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:6\">PRO 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:4\">TIT 2:4</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of children to honour their parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:1–6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of every believer to represent Jesus Christ in the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13\">MAT 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:14\">MAT 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:19–28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility of every human being to love God and others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37-Matt22:39\">MAT 22:37–22:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:29-Mark12:31\">MRK 12:29–12:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:17\">1SA 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:45\">MAT 5:43–5:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:28-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:28–10:37</a></p>\n<h2>The responsibility to exercise dominion over the animal kingdom and creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26\">GEN 1:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:10\">PRO 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:2\">GEN 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:5\">EXO 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:4\">DEU 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:6-Deut22:7\">DEU 22:6–22:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:4\">DEU 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:6-Ps8:8\">PSA 8:6–8:8</a></p>",
